                <p>But don't lose your catnip just yet. Cats offers split symbols, which is just as exciting as watching your furry friend chase after a laser pointer. These split symbols can give you the possibility of getting combinations of up to 10 symbols, because sometimes, one cat just isn't enough. Landing five split symbols across an active payline will give you a grant of 10 symbols. That's right, you get the same thrill as when your cat finally gets that midnight treat.</p>
                <p>And if we're talking about landing big wins, we can't forget about the Panther symbol. This symbol pays the most in the game. So, if you see that panther looking at you all fierce on your screen, don't be scared - just pray that it lands on your payline. </p>"
